note:stream.java uses or overrides a depredacted API. note:Recompile with Xlint-depracation for details. files compiled successfully! press any key to continue..
and co i closed the compiler out and signed back into my server and the welcome is still the same..Any help/suggestions would help me so so much AND ALSO: when the compiler says that did it work? lol
